data.description: Gorgeous two-story with 3 beds/ 2.5 baths, 2120 sqft home in Redland Woods. Recent Updates! the house comes with a brand-new water softener installed in 2020 and a brand-new AC unit installed in 2021, as well as a brand-new oven installed in 2023. The home has an open living and dining room floor plan with a cozy fireplace ready to make memories with your family and friends. The kitchen is spacious with stainless steel appliances. The spacious primary bedroom upstairs has a full bath with a tub & shower combo. Great backyard space with patio slab, privacy fence, and mature trees perfect for gatherings. North East ISD. Welcome Home!
